data.description: ZONED COMMERCIAL - Remodeled by previous owner, meticulous care went into updating this warm and inviting cottage. Numerous updates, beautiful kitchen, with newer appliances. Gas stove, refrigerator, microwave, large detached finished shop/craft building, huge dog palace with it's own pool, koi pond, fully fenced commercial property situated nicely on large 6604 sq ft corner lot. 2 bedrooms and 1 office (easy convert to 3 bedrooms) Truly an oasis    WARNING - Very protective dogs at this property, must be accompanied by your agent or realtor to tour.
